title: MisterMusic Show 360 indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 360 [192 kbps stereo MP3] 2 hours.


A lot of new and recent music on the show this week!
New stuff from Foals, Chappo, The Radio Dept., Yukon Blonde, and Wolf Alice.
And the usual mix of indie, alternative and classic hits from over 5 decades of rock stuck in-between.
We travel back to mid June 1977 for the 'Oldie of the Week'. A song that was number one on the charts 38 years ago.
Broadcast weekly and heard all over the globe, it's The MisterMusic Show, the way radio should be.

The MisterMusic Show is heard on RockXS.com internet radio.
